  "description": {
    "zh": "听好了士兵。去过塔科夫的商务中心了吗？既然你熟悉那地方，我需要你去那儿找一辆带燃油拖挂的卡车。它就藏在地下某处——具体位置我也不清楚，所以你得单干，我可不想派自己的人去送死，不是针对你。找到后记得用标记器标出来，可以借你一个，但别搞丢了。\n\n还有，顺手把周边清干净，别让第三方势力盯上咱们的行动。祝你好运，士兵。",
    "en": "Alright listen up soldier. Been to the business center of Tarkov? I hope you are familiar with the place already because I need someone to go there and look for a fuel trailer. One of my guys told me his group saw a truck carrying fuel in the underground, not sure where that is supposed to be, so you are on your own there since I am against sending my guys down there again, nothing personal.\n\nDon't forget to use one of these markers when you find it, I can lend you one but don't lose it.\n\nAnd one more thing, don't forget to clear out the area a bit while you are at it, we don't want any third parties noticing our little operation here. Good luck soldier."
  },
